entries.journal_entry_description: Investigate recent vandalism at the Coronet starport and bring down the perpetrators.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Demmi Wot is an ex-Ragtag who works with Finn Shallo from time to time. Finn is hoping that Demmi can help you find the Ragtags that are responsible for the starport vandalism.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Demmi Wot needs you to to defeat two squads of Ragtags. Defeat the first of these two squads.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Defeat the First Squad of Ragtags
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The Ragtags are unhappy now. Defeat the second squad of Ragtags.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Defeat the Second Squad of Ragtags
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Now that you have defeated the two Ragtag squads, return to Demmi Wot and talk to him.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Jesseb Convorr at the Coronet starport and let him know that the Ragtags responsible for the vandalism to the starport have answered for their crimes.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Report to Lt. Jasper and brief him on the result of your investigation into the starport vandalism.
